    "mc_media_text_69MnUW": {
      "type": "mc_media-text",
      "blocks": {
        "slide_hqA4tG": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "media_type": "video",
            "media_position": "left",
            "media_size": "fill",
            "video_desktop": "shopify://files/videos/3.mp4",
            "media_ratio": "",
            "mb_media_ratio": "",
            "show_subhead": true,
            "subhead": "Advanced Suspension Smooth Every Ride",
            "subhead_color": "#ff0000",
            "head": "Superior Comfort and Stability",
            "head_color": "#ffffff",
            "head_gradient_color": "",
            "text": "<p>Upgraded inverted hydraulic front fork and nitrogen rear shock, combined with <strong>220 N·m torque</strong>, deliver stable, controlled riding on rugged trails—finished with a <strong>rear brake light</strong> for added safety.</p>",
            "text_color": "#b2b2b2",
            "text_bold_color": "#ff0000"
          }
        },
        "slide_9yB38d": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "media_type": "video",
            "media_position": "right",
            "media_size": "fill",
            "video_desktop": "shopify://files/videos/2.mp4",
            "media_ratio": "",
            "mb_media_ratio": "",
            "show_subhead": true,
            "subhead": "Powerful Motor, Superior Performance",
            "subhead_color": "#ff0000",
            "head": "Enhanced Speed and Maneuverability",
            "head_color": "#ffffff",
            "head_gradient_color": "",
            "text": "<p>The IN 10 Pro delivers<strong> impressive acceleration and unmatched agility</strong>. Its advanced motor technology ensures you glide through streets and trails with ease, while<strong> versatile riding modes and a reverse function</strong> keep you in full command.<br/></p>",
            "text_color": "#b2b2b2",
            "text_bold_color": "#ff0000"
          }
        },
        "slide_RMkFmA": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "media_type": "video",
            "media_position": "left",
            "media_size": "fill",
            "video_desktop": "shopify://files/videos/1.mp4",
            "media_ratio": "",
            "mb_media_ratio": "",
            "show_subhead": true,
            "subhead": "Extended Battery Power for Longer Adventures",
            "subhead_color": "#ff0000",
            "head": "Ride More, Recharge Less",
            "head_color": "#ffffff",
            "head_gradient_color": "",
            "text": "<p>The <strong>60V27Ah</strong> lithium-ion battery now delivers up to <strong>88 km </strong>per charge, surpassing the original IN10. Quick 6–7 hour charging keeps you on the move, supporting riders up to<strong> 120 kg </strong>(330 lbs) on both trails and city roads.</p>",
            "text_color": "#b2b2b2",
            "text_bold_color": "#ff0000"
          }
        }
      },
